title: SKB Universal Banjo Case
features: Universal 4-/5-string Banjo Hardshell Case with Heavy-duty ABS Shell
description: When it's time to hit the road, SKB's 1SKB-50 universal four- or five-string banjo hardshell case is just what you need to keep your closed-back banjo safe from even the harshest conditions. This extremely heavy-duty hardshell case is more than tough enough to protect your banjo from bumps, jolts, and accidental impact. Its plush-lined EPS interior provides you with full-length neck support and features a large internal storage compartment. TSA-approved locks in the 1SKB-50's trigger latches also make it a great flight case. When you need protection you can count on, you need an SKB 1SKB-50 hardshell banjo case.
